    • Method Detail

      • find

        Provider find(java.util.List<Provider> providers,
              Person person,
              HealthRecord.EncounterType service,
              long time)
        Find a provider with a specific service for the person.
        Parameters:
        providers - The list of eligible providers.
        person - The patient who requires the service.
        service - The service required. For example, EncounterType.AMBULATORY.
        time - The date/time within the simulated world, in milliseconds.
        Returns:
        Service provider or null if none is available.
